{"tid":2071332,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"因為愛 所以祝福","createTime":"2020-06-19T17:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T07:39:10.000Z","uid":199552,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b6a7ffeee95c0d95366267b7cf7ff15e32b69379","tid":2071332,"uid":199552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T17:58:38.000Z","msg":"得知前度有新女朋友 <br />\n<br />\n第一個反應係嬲 明明佢話忙所以在學期間都唔會拍拖 亦覺得以前段回憶好唔真實 仲記得你同我講唔會有下個<br />\n<br />\n第二個反應係壓抑 覺得自己要成熟啲 唔可以因衝動喺wts破口大罵 咁樣損人不利己<br />\n<br />\n第三個反應係平靜 原來呢件事冇想像中咁痛苦 <br />\n<br />\n好好記住每段關係學到嘅嘢 <br />\n多謝你教識我上進心、教識我控制情緒、教識我點同異性相處、教識我點愛一個人<br />\n<br />\n希望我地都幸福 <br />\n<br />\n(可能我嘅闊達係扮 但扮扮下可能會變真呢 大個女喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"b637b9de09ff4a49aa02cdc85eb64a892b3a850f","tid":2071332,"uid":287715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:05:30.000Z","msg":"唱翻首 最後祝福 先"},{"pid":"792182b8735ac14baf33524ea65539ef2072a8c9","tid":2071332,"uid":199552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b637b9de09ff4a49aa02cdc85eb64a892b3a850f","tid":2071332,"uid":287715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:05:30.000Z","msg":"唱翻首 最後祝福 先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:08:39.000Z","msg":"太傷感喇哈哈"},{"pid":"f62e31d32daad487757a802ccec2b3b174bd462c","tid":2071332,"uid":317167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b637b9de09ff4a49aa02cdc85eb64a892b3a850f","tid":2071332,"uid":287715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:05:30.000Z","msg":"唱翻首 最後祝福 先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:10:36.000Z","msg":"祝褔聲想你都聽到　可記得當年 <br />\n是我們沒毅力　漸漸行漸漸遠"},{"pid":"5e92cb4770649f68b5b1b52780f9ba272f98fbda","tid":2071332,"uid":199552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f62e31d32daad487757a802ccec2b3b174bd462c","tid":2071332,"uid":317167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b637b9de09ff4a49aa02cdc85eb64a892b3a850f","tid":2071332,"uid":287715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s